Competitor analysis & benchmarking.

Niche domination: own a segment before expansion.

Pricing & value strategies to outmaneuver rivals.

Customer loyalty systems: retention > acquisition.

Strategic alliances: partnerships to expand influence.

Negotiation & influence at high-stakes levels.

Crisis exploitation: turning challenges into opportunities.



